channel.title: My server can't get online... WTF!
channel.description: OK, when I try to get my server, which is a PimpScape based server, it always tells me the server's online eventhough it is CLEARLY online... When I go to put it on the server status page, that's where it always tells me it's always offline.. Can someone help me here? Would seriously appreciate, thanks!
